robotUSB
========
BadUSB sketch for Arduino that canNOT be used for malicious purposes.
NEVER try to use it outside of virtual machines.

wnd.ino - windows version of robotUSB
lnx.ino - linux version of robotUSB
mac.ino - macOS version of robotUSB
hex.ino - hexOS version of robotUSB (github.com/riotoff/hex)

